text: Younger Now is the sixth studio album by Miley Cyrus. It was released on 29 September 2017 through RCA Records. It features guest appearance of Dolly Parton. It went to number 1 in Spain and the top 20 in Australia, Austria, Canada, Czech Republic, Germany, Ireland, Italy, Mexico, the Netherlands, New Zealand, Norway, Poland, Portugal, Scotland, Slovakia, Sweden, Switzerland, the United Kingdom and the United States. ==Track listing== All tracks are written by Miley Cyrus and Oren Yoel, except where noted. ==References== Category:2017 albums Category:Miley Cyrus albums
title: Younger Now
